</para> </listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
The UseGlobbing directive controls use of glob() functionality, which is
needed for supporting wildcard characters such as *.</para>
</refsect1>

